{"id":69017,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Batman_Begins","text":"\"Batman Begins\" is a 2005 superhero movie directed by Christopher Nolan and written by Nolan and David S. Goyer. Based on the fictional DC Comics character Batman, it stars Christian Bale, Michael Caine, Gary Oldman, Liam Neeson, Katie Holmes, Cillian Murphy, Tom Wilkinson, Rutger Hauer, Ken Watanabe, and Morgan Freeman. The movie reboots the \"Batman movie series\", telling the origin story of Bruce Wayne from the death of his parents to his journey to become Batman and his fight to stop Ra's al Ghul and the Scarecrow from plunging Gotham City into chaos.\n\"Batman Begins\" was successful, and in 2008 a sequel titled \"The Dark Knight\" was released.\n\"Batman Begins\" was the first movie in Christopher Nolan's \"The Dark Knight Trilogy\".","categories":[],"infobox_types":["movie"],"annotations":[{"uri":"2005_in_movies","surface_form":"2005","offset":21},{"uri":"Superhero","surface_form":"superhero","offset":26},{"uri":"Movie","surface_form":"movie","offset":36},{"uri":"Christopher_Nolan","surface_form":"Christopher Nolan","offset":54},{"uri":"David_S._Goyer","surface_form":"David S. Goyer","offset":97},{"uri":"Fictional_character","surface_form":"fictional","offset":126},{"uri":"DC_Comics","surface_form":"DC Comics","offset":136},{"uri":"Batman","surface_form":"Batman","offset":156},{"uri":"Christian_Bale","surface_form":"Christian Bale","offset":173},{"uri":"Michael_Caine","surface_form":"Michael Caine","offset":189},{"uri":"Gary_Oldman","surface_form":"Gary Oldman","offset":204},{"uri":"Liam_Neeson","surface_form":"Liam Neeson","offset":217},{"uri":"Katie_Holmes","surface_form":"Katie Holmes","offset":230},{"uri":"Cillian_Murphy","surface_form":"Cillian Murphy","offset":244},{"uri":"Tom_Wilkinson","surface_form":"Tom Wilkinson","offset":260},{"uri":"Rutger_Hauer","surface_form":"Rutger Hauer","offset":275},{"uri":"Ken_Watanabe","surface_form":"Ken Watanabe","offset":289},{"uri":"Morgan_Free